title: 2007–08 Icelandic Hockey League season
text: The 2007-08 <a href="Icelandic%20Hockey%20League">Icelandic Hockey League</a> season was the 17th season of the Icelandic Hockey League, the top level of ice hockey in <a href="Iceland">Iceland</a>. Four teams participated in the league, and Skautafelag Akureyrar won the championship.
